                            <comment id="70465" author="emoly.liu" created="Fri, 1 Nov 2013 08:34:59 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/8132&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/8132&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
